        <footer>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row footer-widgets">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="footer-widget mail-subscribe-widget">
                            <b>M/S Avani Paridhi Energy & Communications (P) Ltd.</b> is a company registered as per Companies Registration act India. M/s APEC is also an ISO 9001 certified company.
